     Z S E R I O  C + +  R E F L E C T I O N


Java Extension
==============

https://github.com/Klebert-Engineering/zserio-cpp-introspection

Build
=====

> mkdir build && cd build
> cmake -DZSERIO_RT_DIR=<path-to-zserio-cpp-rt-dir> ..
> cmake --build .

The build expects a zserio binary in your PATH env.
Basic wrapper script:

> #!/bin/sh
> java -jar <path-to-zserio-jar> $@

Test
====

> ctest --verbose

Hacking
=======

Use the ./format script to apply cmake-format on all sources.

Sources under /zsr are public, sources under /src are private.
